---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import InfoPageLayout from '../../layouts/InfoPageLayout.astro'
import contentImage from '../../assets/Commercial-New.jpg';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <InfoPageLayout>
    <Fragment slot="pageTag">Building the Future of Your Business</Fragment>
    <Fragment slot="pageDetails">
      Every successful business starts with a solid foundation in both vision and construction. 
      Whether you're opening a new storefront, building an office space, or creating a large-scale 
      commercial facility, the right construction team is essential to bringing your business to life.
      Whether you're starting from scratch or expanding your company, we are here to turn your vision into reality.
    </Fragment>
    <img slot="heroImage" src={contentImage.src} alt="Windows and doors" />
  </InfoPageLayout>
</BaseLayout>
